{"tid":1534013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【攬炒？】澳門9月賭收料錄中低單位數升幅","createTime":"2019-09-03T01:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T00:31:05.000Z","uid":236171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cf338896b0ca54f36ddf67148586f1e9e221b320","tid":1534013,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">究竟點解香港澳門會一齊淡市嘅？</span></strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n澳門大量旅客係去香港順道過嚟，<br />\n要不是香港人澳門早就完蛋了？<br />\n<br />\n定係<br />\n<br />\n絕大部分旅遊業跌幅都係關貿易戰事<br />\n香港近期事件根本對旅遊業冇乜影響？<br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">澳門9月賭收料錄中低單位數升幅</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20190903/s00004/1567450023553/%e6%be%b3%e9%96%809%e6%9c%88%e8%b3%ad%e6%94%b6-%e6%96%99%e9%8c%84%e4%b8%ad%e4%bd%8e%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e6%95%b8%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20190903%2Fs00004%2F1567450023553%2F%25e6%25be%25b3%25e9%2596%25809%25e6%259c%2588%25e8%25b3%25ad%25e6%2594%25b6-%25e6%2596%2599%25e9%258c%2584%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e4%25bd%258e%25e5%2596%25ae%25e4%25bd%258d%25e6%2595%25b8%25e5%258d%2587%25e5%25b9%2585&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=11b8ed18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20190903%2Fs00004%2F1567450023553%2F%25e6%25be%25b3%25e9%2596%25809%25e6%259c%2588%25e8%25b3%25ad%25e6%2594%25b6-%25e6%2596%2599%25e9%258c%2584%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e4%25bd%258e%25e5%2596%25ae%25e4%25bd%258d%25e6%2595%25b8%25e5%258d%2587%25e5%25b9%2585&h=a3e347ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20190903/s00004/1567450023553/%e6%be%b3%e9%96%809%e6%9c%88%e8%b3%ad%e6%94%b6-%e6%96%99%e9%8c%84%e4%b8%ad%e4%bd%8e%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e6%95%b8%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】澳門博彩監察協調局最新公布的8月賭收按年跌8.6%，只有242.62億澳門元，多家大行均認為，賭收表現差過預期，主要受貴賓博彩持續疲弱及香港連串示威活動影響。踏入9月，因為沒有如去年颱風山竹吹襲令賭場停止營運的影響，大行普遍預期9月賭收會有低至中位的單位數字增幅，當中摩根大通預期，9月賭收會有1％至2%增幅。<br />\n<br />\n由於8月賭收表現遜於預期，除新濠國際（0200）昨日股價微升逾0.3%，其餘皆下跌，跌幅最大為澳博（0880），下跌2.8%。藍籌股金沙中國（1928）及銀河娛樂（0027）分別跌2.11%及1.02%。<br />\n<br />\n澳博金沙昨跌逾2%<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀指出，8月賭收表現差過預期，主要與貴賓博彩疲弱有關，並且受到太陽城7月份被官媒點名批評事件影響，致月內貴賓博彩收入按年跌25％至30%，但料9月沒有如去年颱風山竹吹襲而令賭場需要停止營運33小時的影響，因此估計9月的賭收可以錄得持平或有低的單位數增長。摩根大通稱，8月賭收表現除受貴賓博彩表現拖累，亦受香港的示威活動影響，展望9月份賭收有1％至2%增長。瑞信認為，即使8月賭收較差，不見得會影響濠賭股盈利表現。"},{"pid":"db1d39e2dd7203f6412426561fe2a0d9b8a7e41e","tid":1534013,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75f83db56823c587a1e09c8aef68e489ce9d186","tid":1534013,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:30:46.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/